
<h3>75th SUOC Reunion Registration</h3>
<p>
Welcome to the registration page for the SUOC 75th Reunion.<br/>This page is only for signing up and paying. 
Please go to reunion site
<a href="http://suocoldtimers.org">http://suocoldtimers.org</a> for continuing updates.
<p>
If you want to see who's going, click <a href="http://suoc.syr.edu/reunion/who">here</a>.
</p>
<table>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<b>Notice to Procrastinators!</b>
<P>
We have already ordered the T-Shirts! We ordered a little bit more than people who registered, but not much more. 
Suzie LaMont, the TShirt Girl, informs us that XL, 2X and 3X TShirts are now sold out. What are you people eating?!?!
</td>
</tr>
<% if @self_registered %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<h2>Congratulations! <%= current_user.name %> is registered for the 75th Reunion!</h2>
We have you on record as registering for the SUOC 75th Reunion.
You may still register other people you may be bringing.
</td>
</tr>
<% end %>

<% if !@registrants.empty? %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
You have the following items under your name:
<% @registrants.each do |r| %>
<%= render :partial => "item", :collection => r.items %>
<% end %>
</td>
</tr>
<% end %>

<% if !@registrants.empty? %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
Please go to <a href="http://suocoldtimers.org">http://suocoldtimers.org</a> to contact somebody if you need to cancel and need a refund.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<hr/>
</td>
</tr>
<% end %>

<% if ! @self_registered %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<h2>Register for the Event of the Century!</h2>
</td>
</tr>
<% end %>

<tr>
<td><img alt="Step 1" src="/images/Step1.gif"></td>
<% if ! @self_registered %>
<td colspan="5">Register Yourself. Please select T-Shirt Size.</td>
</tr>
<%= render :partial => "self_registration_add_cart" %>
<% else %>
<td colspan="5">You're already registered!!.</td>
</tr>
<% end %>

<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<hr/>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><img alt="Step 2" src="/images/Step2.gif"></td>
<td colspan="4">Register any kids and guests you will be paying for.</td>
</tr>
<%= render :partial => "guest_registration_add_cart" %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<hr/>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><img alt="Step 3" src="/images/Step3.gif"></td>
<td colspan="1">Add any extra tshirts you might want.</td>
<td><a href="images/TShirts.gif"><img src="images/TShirts.gif" width="200" height="70"/></a><br>Click image to enlarge.</td>
</tr>
<%= render :partial => "x_tshirt" %>
<tr>
<td colspan="5">
<hr/>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><img alt="Step 4" src="/images/Step4.gif"></td>
<td colspan="4">Review your shopping cart and checkout, if you haven't already.<br/>
Please make sure that you did Step 1.
</td>
</tr>
<%= render :partial => "view_cart" %>

</table>
